    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s got some miles of memories on it, but it's still looking sharp and ready for many more adventures! Come take it for a spin, I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
