    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example features a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including VANOS solenoid service and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the communicative feedback and balanced weight distribution this platform is famous for. While it shows honest signs of use, the drivetrain remains robust and the power delivery is exceptionally linear.",
