    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a reliable and refined driving experience. The exterior paint retains a brilliant gloss, complemented by original alloy wheels in excellent shape, though close inspection reveals a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium seating shows only light softening on the driver-side bolster, while the carpets and dashboard remain in superb condition. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced regularly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring the vehicle is road-trip ready with plenty of tread left on the tires. This is a complete, well-documented car that balances aesthetic appeal with mechanical integrity.",
